{"tid":840104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五星共產寺持有人魏明仁傳昨夜潛逃香港","createTime":"2018-09-28T12:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T14:04:16.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c40c5417411b7d669cf1f5fcaf7e718313d7f042","tid":840104,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2564769_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2564769_2.jpg&h=446dd995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魏明仁26日拆除日升完五星旗後就未現身，外傳恐出境到香港。（記者陳冠備攝）<br />\n2018-09-28 17:54<br />\n〔記者陳冠備／彰化報導〕真的嚇跑了！？「五星共產寺」進行拆除第3天，持有人魏明仁就不再露臉，近日有人外傳魏明仁支付不了500萬拆除費，昨（27日）夜已經潛逃到香港，拆除費恐全民買單！對此彰化縣政府表示，產權所有人其實是魏明仁姊姊魏素丹，拆除完畢後將祭出處分書給所有權人強制執行，不執行就管收。而今日也傳出魏明仁現身拆除現場，經證實只有平時座車出現，他並沒有在車上。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2564769_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2564769_1.jpg&h=cae2de76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 彰化之恥「五星共產寺」已被拆成斷垣殘壁。（記者陳冠備攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2564769_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2564769_3.jpg&h=88c7d90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有民眾擔心，500萬拆除費恐全民買單。（記者陳冠備攝）<br />\n<br />\n「五星共產寺」違建屬實，依法拆除，龐大的拆除費必須由產權所有人負責，然而魏明仁未被限制出境，坊間傳出26日進行拆除隔日他就潛逃到香港，拆除費用恐討不回來。<br />\n<br />\n彰化縣建設處長劉玉平說，估計拆除費用約500萬，依建築法第96條之1規定，由建築物所有權人負擔，真正所有權人是魏明仁姊姊魏素丹，縣府將開立代履行拆除費用行政處分書予魏素丹，如果魏素丹逾期（約2星期）不繳納，即可移送行政執行署強制執行。<br />\n<br />\n彰化地檢署襄閱主任檢察官黃淑媛表示，魏明仁目前因日前妨害公務罪移送，但已獲交保，去年有一傷害案件遭起訴，兩案件都在偵查，並未對其通緝與限制出境處分。田中分局分局長鄭穎聰說，上午員警則掌握一部魏明仁座車在工地附近徘迴，不過經確認，座車上的人並非魏明仁，烏龍一場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2564769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564769&d=D7p7yELdsgYnL284KuL%2F7F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c6bfe64d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564769&h=504b9baa\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2564769</a><br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278e788ed1d3867f8db5585a6ba9513b661ed341","tid":840104,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"不要讓共狗跑掉"},{"pid":"76b5e5086b7f8fdd138fb4621fd8be0d3c500411","tid":840104,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"即係真係匪諜"},{"pid":"f0acb8cb2138180756bf82e17cfd3c06b23d110e","tid":840104,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"台灣好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad731b8defaeb5a96eed7f2b938071ec886606c4","tid":840104,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"幾時輪到天安門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}